      <title>特朗普出生公民权令遭法官暂时阻止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/us-judge-temporarily-blocks-trump-birthright-citizenship-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官暂时阻止唐纳德·特朗普总统限制谁有资格在出生时自动获得美国公民身份，这对新政府强硬的移民议程来说是一个早期的法律挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/us-judge-temporarily-blocks-trump-birthright-citizenship-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 18:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉顾问力图模仿谢因鲍姆对特朗普的“冷静”态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/lula-advisers-aim-to-mimic-sheinbaum-s-cool-approach-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克劳迪娅·希恩鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 为阻止唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对墨西哥的无情攻击所做的努力赢得了巴西人的崇拜者，并促使她的一位盟友考虑效仿她对付这位好斗的美国领导人的方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/lula-advisers-aim-to-mimic-sheinbaum-s-cool-approach-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 18:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望中国帮助迫使普京达成协议结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-looks-to-china-to-help-press-putin-into-a-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他正寻求与中国合作达成解决方案，以此向总统弗拉基米尔·普京施加压力，迫使其通过谈判达成一项结束俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-looks-to-china-to-help-press-putin-into-a-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 18:01:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农业部长提名人支持特朗普大规模驱逐计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/agriculture-secretary-nominee-backs-trump-mass-deportation-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普提名的农业部长布鲁克·罗林斯支持总统“大规模驱逐”计划，此举可能会损害严重依赖外国劳动力的美国农民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/agriculture-secretary-nominee-backs-trump-mass-deportation-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 17:45:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向莫尼汉抱怨美国银行阻挠保守派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-surprises-davos-alleges-top-us-banks-reject-conservatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普出人意料地对美国银行公司首席执行官布莱恩·莫伊尼汉进行了猛烈批评，斥责他并出其不意地声称该银行限制与保守派客户的业务往来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-surprises-davos-alleges-top-us-banks-reject-conservatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队考虑任命凯尔·巴斯担任财政部或国防职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-team-considering-kyle-bass-for-a-treasury-or-defense-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，特朗普政府正在考虑任命对冲基金资深人士、对华鹰派凯尔巴斯 (Kyle Bass) 担任财政部或国防部的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-team-considering-kyle-bass-for-a-treasury-or-defense-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在达沃斯呼吁降低油价、降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-urges-opec-to-lower-oil-prices-warns-of-tariffs-at-davos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周四在达沃斯向世界各国领导人发表讲话时表示，他将要求沙特阿拉伯和其他石油输出国组织国家“降低石油成本”，并重申他将利用关税将制造业带回美国的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-urges-opec-to-lower-oil-prices-warns-of-tariffs-at-davos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普经济风险下马丁重返爱尔兰总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰共和党领袖迈克尔·马丁 (Micheal Martin) 在去年 11 月的选举中当选为总理，主要现任执政联盟伙伴重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利称将就欧盟对俄罗斯制裁延期与美国磋商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/eu-russia-sanctions-in-limbo-as-orban-aide-calls-for-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利表示，由于本月底是最后期限，它将在决定是否延长欧盟对俄罗斯的制裁之前与美国磋商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/eu-russia-sanctions-in-limbo-as-orban-aide-calls-for-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 10:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关注运河问题 卢比奥将首次出访巴拿马</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/marco-rubio-plans-to-visit-panama-as-trump-eyes-canal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥计划于下周晚些时候开始访问拉丁美洲，并访问巴拿马，凸显了唐纳德·特朗普总统收回巴拿马运河的认真态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/marco-rubio-plans-to-visit-panama-as-trump-eyes-canal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 02:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
